Class Servers

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.restaurant.rakshith.Servers
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<Servers>

    public final class Servers
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<Servers>
    Created by Rakshith on 3/17/2017. This class is responsible for the servers object in the restaurant. This class supports Cloning, Comparing. The static field addServerIndex must be initialized as soon as declared. This field is imperative to create a new Servers object. cloning performs a deep copy of the Servers object.
